            }
            
            .quote {
                font-style :italic;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>

    <h2>Famous quotes</h2>
    <p class="quote">
    "My mama always said life was like a box of chocolates. You never know what you're gonna get.".
    <br> - Forrest Gump
    </p>
    
    <p class="quote">
